						<summary>

						<p>Records the scale of money payments agreed to be paid by the merchants and other people of <hi rend="bold">Anuppalli,</hi> to the temple of Gōpālasvāmi and Hanumantarāya and to their priests. The village is stated to be situated in Jagadāpi-Gutti-<hi rend="italic">sīma.</hi></p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

